> 
> ```
> namespace Shapes {
>   export namespace Polygons {
>     export class Triangle {}
>     export class Square {}
>   }
> }
> ```

that's typescript syntax, not JS syntax tho

I would really like to see some syntax like what exists in Rust to import from the enclosing "parent" module
```rs
#[cfg(test)]
mod tests {
  use super::*;
}
```

